==English==

===Etymology===
From Latin, from Greekk ''[[phantasmoophobia]]'' literally "fear of ghosts", from ''[[phantasma]]'' "ghost" + ''[[phobos]]'' "fear".

===Noun===
'''phantasmophobia'''
# An abnormal or irrational fear of [[ghost]]s and [[phantom]]s.

====Related terms====
*[[phantasmophobic]]

